Trina Michaels is struggling. In her last match she lost to the lowest ranked wrestler we had. However she has amazing booming tits! But lets give credit where credit is due: Trina never gives up, never gives in, and she fights to the last whistle every match.
Welcome Bella Rossi who brings her natural 34DD breasts to the mat. Bella is a local girl who came with a friend and sat in the audience for a tag team match. Afterward she approached us to wrestle, and here she is! The heaviest of our welterweights, Bella is looking to carve out a name for herself on US.
